---
title: Cheesy Beef Burger & Fries with Rosemary Caramelised Onion & Truffle Mayo
description: Get your napkins ready – this is one seriously juicy burger! We've loaded it with flavour, from the rosemary-infused caramelised onion to the truffle mayo and melted Cheddar, so that every bite will take you to your happy place.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-beef-burger-truffle-mayo-9a32fcdd.jpg
